    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving as if it just left the dealership. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom state with no signs of wear or aging. Every feature functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. A rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle in pristine, collector-grade condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
